sequenceDiagram
    participant Grid as #store-grid
    participant Card as .product-card
    participant Button as button.btn
    participant Handler as Event Handler
    
    Note over Grid,Handler: User clicks "Add to Cart" button
    
    Button->>Button: event.target = button
    Note over Button: textContent: "Add to Cart"
    
    Button->>Card: Event bubbles up
    Note over Card: event.currentTarget could be .product-card<br/>if listener attached here
    
    Card->>Grid: Event bubbles up
    Note over Grid: event.currentTarget could be #store-grid<br/>if using event delegation
    
    Grid->>Handler: Event reaches delegated listener
    Handler->>Handler: Check event.target matches<br/>"button.btn"
    Handler->>Handler: Find product data<br/>Update cart count<br/>Adjust stock
    
    Note over Grid,Handler: Event delegation: 1 listener for many buttons!
